Syncfusion Essential Studio
Essential Studio now offers complete support for the implementation of the all-new Microsoft Office 2007 user interface in your .NET applications.
Multiple ribbon-tabs just like those in Office 2007, Quick buttons, Menu buttons, SuperToolTips and Accelerators will all be provided out of the box. As with every Syncfusion control, complete design time support will be available. Enabling Office 2007 features in your application will require very little code.
All New ContextMenuStripEx, StatusBarStrip, TrackBarEx with Office 2007 Style by default, Galleries, MiniToolBar are released for v.5.1.
